public interface Secs1OnTcpIpCommunicator
extends Secs1Communicator, Secs1OnTcpIpLogObservable
This instance is implementation of SECS-I (SEMI-E4) on TCP/IP.
  • To create new instance, newInstance(Secs1OnTcpIpCommunicatorConfig)
  • To create new instance and open, open(Secs1OnTcpIpCommunicatorConfig)
